Andrea Yates, from Clear Lake, Texas, was convicted of capital murder in 2002 .
She drowned her children Noah, 7, John, 5; Paul, 3; Luke, 2; and Mary, 6 .
Her ex-husband Russell 'Rusty' Yates slammed her murder trial as the 'cruelest thing he had ever witnessed'
He insisted her actions were 'completely a result of her illness'
She was found not guilty by reason of insanity and sentenced to life in prison .